<paragraph id="2BCC3877C7F763B9B2B9EF3725C05745" pageNumber="40">
<taxonomicName id="261CC1ADBB55CB3A77DFB9340112F589" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Diplolepis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Diplolepis Steindachner 1863</taxonomicName>
: 2 (type species by original designation: 
<taxonomicName id="677B08D168791D3873EC8661E4BB8724" class="Actinopterygii" family="Sciaenidae" genus="Sciaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageNumber="40" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="squamosissima">Sciaena squamosissima Heckel 1840</taxonomicName>
