<taxonomicName id="EE2FBFEBAD2E547D66599763A8EFDECE" class="Actinopterygii" family="Sciaenidae" genus="Plagioscion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageNumber="41" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="ternetzi">P. ternetzi</taxonomicName>
